d-or-considered","fullItemName":"Scenario: Managing a child or young person where maltreatment is suspected or considered"}]},{"id":"6f3c598e-b6a6-55f1-ad89-fdd4b15f6ca5","fullItemName":"Supporting evidence","slug":"supporting-evidence","subChapters":[]},{"id":"9759c4be-58ba-5252-b7c6-e9b62b19cd6a","fullItemName":"How this topic was developed","slug":"how-this-topic-was-developed","subChapters":[{"id":"697d1866-8032-5002-91c8-dc3eeca58727","slug":"search-strategy","fullItemName":"Search strategy"},{"id":"361bdae4-265e-5b25-acd3-bf844a2d39c9","slug":"stakeholder-engagement","fullItemName":"Stakeholder engagement"},{"id":"d8109ffa-0f7a-5572-93a9-610b5fe4defc","slug":"evidence-exclusion-criteria","fullItemName":"Evidence exclusion criteria"},{"id":"94f7c98a-764f-5d31-b3a3-b2d93239a6d6","slug":"organizational-behavioural-financial-barriers","fullItemName":"Organizational, behavioural and financial barriers"},{"id":"0739870f-84b7-51ea-8cc6-e5e9512edf71","slug":"declarations-of-interest","fullItemName":"Declarations of interest"}]},{"id":"8e451184-169a-5b06-a497-ca543bbd9ebb","fullItemName":"References","slug":"references","subChapters":[]}]},"parentChapter":{"id":"c0bafcc6-8752-50c3-8db0-d50d07b4b32c","slug":"recognition","fullItemName":"Recognition"},"subChapters":[{"id":"0cb3e65a-f900-58ce-92f9-4b5fe59a2b84","slug":"basis-for-recommendation-83b","fullItemName":"Basis for recommendation","depth":3,"htmlHeader":"<!-- begin field 6e24493b-a4f2-428f-896a-ff142a5515bb --><h3>Basis for recommendation</h3><!-- end field 6e24493b-a4f2-428f-896a-ff142a5515bb -->","summary":null,"htmlStringContent":"<!-- begin item 83bd2aed-1141-4d23-9615-85a8da3f82a6 --><!-- begin field 31d6af85-3948-4596-8552-e035a49e9288 --><p>The information on when to suspect fabricated or induced illness is based on expert opinion in the National Institute for Health and Care Excellence (NICE) guidelines <em>Child abuse and neglect </em>[<a class=\"bibliography-reference internal-reference\" href=\"/topics/child-maltreatment-recognition-management/references/\">NICE, 2017b</a>] and <em>Child maltreatment: when to suspect maltreatment in under 18s</em> [<a class=\"bibliography-reference internal-reference\" href=\"/topics/child-maltreatment-recognition-management/references/\">NICE, 2017a</a>].</p><!-- end field 31d6af85-3948-4596-8552-e035a49e9288 --><!-- end item 83bd2aed-1141-4d23-9615-85a8da3f82a6 -->","subChapters":[]}]}}},"staticQueryHashes":["3666801979"]}